Package com.ppm.integration.agilesdk.epic

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PortfolioEpicCreationInfo
    Class used by PPM to pass the information of the Epic to be created in the Agile Project.
    PortfolioEpicIntegration
    Main class of Portfolio Epic integration point, used to push Portfolio Epic from PPM to the agile tool.
    PortfolioEpicSyncInfo
    Class used when the Portfolio Epic information is synched from the Agile Project to PPM (progress, Story Points sizing, ...).
